요." resource-id="" class="android.widget.TextView" package="com.samsung.android.oneconnect" content-desc="" checkable="false" checked="false" clickable="false" enabled="true" focusable="false" focused="false" scrollable="false" long-clickable="false" password="false" selected="false" bounds="[84,2496][996,2496]" /><node index="4" text="Step 2" resource-id="" class="android.widget.TextView" package="com.samsung.android.oneconnect" content-desc="" checkable="false" checked="false" clickable="false" enabled="true" focusable="false" focused="false" scrollable="false" long-clickable="false" password="false" selected="false" bounds="[84,2496][996,2496]" /><node index="5" text="슬라이스햄, 오이, 당근, 양파, 사과는 모두 곱게 채썰어주세요. 양파가 매운맛이 나면 찬물에 잠시 담궜다 사용하세요." resource-id="" class="android.widget.TextView" package="com.samsung.android.oneconnect" content-desc="" checkable="false" checked="false" clickable="false" enabled="true" focusable="false" focused="false" scrollable="false" long-clickable="false" password="false" selected="false" bounds="[84,2496][972,2496]" /><node index="6" text="Step 3" resource-id="" class="android.widget.TextView" package="com.samsung.android.oneconnect" content-desc="" checkable="false" checked="false" clickable="false" enabled="true" focusable="false" focused="false" scrollable="false" long-clickable="false" password="false" selected="false" bounds="[84,2496][996,2496]" /><node index="7" text="볼에 물기뺀 양배추, 햄, 오이, 당근, 양파, 사과를 골고루 섞고, 소스재료를 분량대로 섞어 양배추샐러드를 만들어요." resource-id="" class="android.widget.TextView" package="com.samsung.android.oneconnect" content-desc="" checkable="false" checked="false" clickable="false" enabled="true" focusable="false" focused="false" scrollable="false" long-clickable="false" password="false" selected="false" bounds="[84,2496][963,2496]" /><node index="8" text="Step 4" resource-id="" class="android.widget.TextView" package="com.samsung.android.oneconnect" content-desc="" checkable="false" checked="false" clickable="false" enabled="t